domain

Class PhysicalFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • domain.PhysicalFile

  • public class PhysicalFile
extends java.lang.Object
    PhysicalFile is a representation of a File and the different qualities it has, such as the name, the path, a relative path, the extension. It also contains the content of that file and that content can be compressed and decompressed. Every time a compress or decompression is made, the content of the PhysicalFile changes.
